snippet.title: Dino Run (English)
snippet.description:
Roarrr! Welcome to the epic world of "Dino Run," where a mischievous dinosaur is on the loose and stops at nothing and no one. Join our hilarious dino as he runs through a prehistoric playground, dodging walls, fences, and even crossing bridges like a boss!

DOWNLOAD NOW!!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.moaixstudios.dinorun
